CP IPA+90 DR+
CC X+1.1811 Y-0.315
CP IPA+1800 Z-0.1969 DR+ FQ50
CC X+1.1811 Y-0.315
CP IPA+360 DR+
CC X+1.2514 Y-0.315
CP IPA+90 DR+ FQ54
L X+1.2326 Y-0.2775
CC X+1.2326 Z-0.1594
CP IPA+90 DR+
L X+1.1951 Z+0.6299 FMAX
M9
M5
L M140 MB MAX
M30
END PGM 1234 INCH
